XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Collection of tools to assist in gettext translations
 PyG3T, the Python GetText Translation Toolkit, is a collection of
 tools for computer assisted translation using GNU gettext.
 .
 PyG3T consists of the following tools:
 .
  * gtgrep: script for performing grep-like operations on po-file entries
  * gtxml: script for checking xml in translations
  * podiff: script for generating diffs of po-files
  * poabc: script for checking common translation errors
  * gtparse: module for parsing po-files
 .
 See https://launchpad.net/pyg3t